    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for a buyer looking for a project or a source of parts. The engine is currently struggling with significant performance issues and visible fluid leaks, while the transmission exhibits noticeable slipping. Externally, the body shows several large dents, patches of rust, and faded paint. The interior also requires a complete overhaul due to heavy wear and tear on the upholstery. It is recommended that the buyer hauls the vehicle away as it is not currently reliable for long-distance driving.",
