      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm looking for a new home for this reliable beauty. It\u2019s been so good to me and still runs like a total dream! It\u2019s in great shape and ready to hit the road for its next big adventure. If you're looking for a solid, well-loved ride that won't let you down, this is the one. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat and tell you more about it!",
      "price": 31500.0,
